## 2. Database Entity Relationship Diagram (ERD)

The database schema is mapped by JPA entities with the following structure:

```mermaid
erDiagram
    users {
        Long id PK
        String name
        String email UK
        String password
        String role
        LocalDateTime created_at
    }
    jobs {
        Long id PK
        String title
