## 3. API Endpoints Reference

The backend exposes the following REST API endpoints:

### Authentication (`/api/auth`)
| HTTP Method | Endpoint | Description | Access Level |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/signup` | Register a new user (`SignupRequest`) | Public |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/login` | Login and get JWT (`LoginRequest`) | Public |

### Jobs (`/api/jobs`)
| HTTP Method | Endpoint | Description | Access Level |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `POST` | `/api/jobs/post` | Post a new job posting (`JobRequest`) | Authenticated (Intended: Recruiter) |
| `GET` | `/api/jobs/all` | Retrieve all job listings | Public |
| `GET` | `/api/jobs/my` | Retrieve recruiter's posted jobs | Authenticated (Intended: Recruiter) |
| `DELETE` | `/api/jobs/{id}` | Delete a job by ID | Authenticated Owner (Recruiter) |

### Job Applications (`/api/applications`)
| HTTP Method | Endpoint | Description | Access Level |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `POST` | `/api/applications/apply/{jobId}` | Apply to a job (`ApplicationRequest`) | Authenticated (Intended: Candidate) |
| `GET` | `/api/applications/my` | View authenticated candidate's applications | Authenticated (Intended: Candidate) |
| `GET` | `/api/applications/job/{jobId}` | View all applications for a job | Authenticated Owner (Recruiter) |
| `PUT` | `/api/applications/{id}/status` | Update status (`StatusUpdateRequest`) | Authenticated Owner (Recruiter) |
| `DELETE` | `/api/applications/{id}/withdraw` | Withdraw/delete job application | Authenticated Owner (Candidate) |
| `GET` | `/api/applications/dashboard/candidate` | Statistics map for candidate dashboard | Authenticated (Intended: Candidate) |

